81
00:09:11,550 --> 00:09:12,390
Brother!

82
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,240
Brother, you're okay now.

83
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:27,150
You are my sister?

84
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:34,560
Jianhao,

85
00:09:34,570 --> 00:09:35,630
think carefully.

86
00:09:35,910 --> 00:09:37,840
I don't believe
you would even forget Qing'er.

87
00:09:39,630 --> 00:09:40,790
And who are you?

88
00:09:41,270 --> 00:09:42,270
Wei Jianhao,

89
00:09:42,510 --> 00:09:43,840
do you only remember me?

90
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:45,790
I'm Xia Changyin.

91
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:47,560
I...

92
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,000
I'm sorry

93
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,790
I only remember Sister Wan'er.

94
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:55,840
You...

95
00:09:58,570 --> 00:10:00,890
It must be because he and Wan'er
were cultivating together,

96
00:10:01,390 --> 00:10:03,440
