100
00:10:25,940 --> 00:10:28,340
(Wei Shop)

101
00:10:35,630 --> 00:10:36,470
Jianhao.

102
00:10:36,910 --> 00:10:37,750
Sister Lili.

103
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,240
Is Sister Wan'er here?

104
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,440
Wan'er is asleep.

105
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:44,720
What do you want with her?

106
00:10:44,870 --> 00:10:46,000
Should I go wake her up?

107
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,630
No, there's no need.

108
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:50,000
Then I'll come back tomorrow.

109
00:10:51,510 --> 00:10:52,350
Wait!

110
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,360
Is there anything else?

111
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,390
Don't get me wrong.

112
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,670
