113
00:11:09,170 --> 00:11:10,010
Thanks.

114
00:11:10,020 --> 00:11:10,880
You're welcome.

115
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,270
However, I think

116
00:11:13,550 --> 00:11:15,600
Sister Wan'er prefers
this style of mine.

117
00:11:19,290 --> 00:11:20,960
♪Trying to tell♪

118
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:23,910
It's quite nice too.

119
00:11:24,910 --> 00:11:25,750
Alright.

120
00:11:25,870 --> 00:11:27,390
Then I'll come to Wan'er tomorrow.

121
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,600
You should also rest early, Sister Lili.

122
00:11:29,610 --> 00:11:32,850
♪But we're only friends♪

123
00:11:35,020 --> 00:11:38,620
♪How can friends hold hands♪

124
00:11:39,030 --> 00:11:44,030
♪All I have is greetings♪

125
00:11:45,810 --> 00:11:47,490
♪You're not♪

126
00:11:47,700 --> 00:11:50,800
♪That good with him♪

127
00:11:53,940 --> 00:11:55,660
♪In fact♪

128
